flowchart LR
  Inputs[Environment Interface / Inputs] --> Context[Context Layer / Grounding]
  Context --> State[State / Memory / Knowledge Store]
  State --> Decision[Decision Engine]
  Decision --> Plan[Planning / Policy / Reasoning]
  Plan --> Action[Action And Tool Execution]
  Action --> Monitor[Monitoring / Logging / Audit Trail]
  Monitor --> Feedback[Feedback / Evaluation / Learning Loop]
  Feedback --> State

  Governance[Governance] --> Context
  Governance --> Decision
  Governance --> Action
  Governance --> Monitor

  Human[Human Approval / Escalation] --> Action
  Kill[Kill Switch / Fallback] --> Action
  Security[Security / Privacy / Prompt Injection Controls] --> Inputs
  Security --> Context
  Security --> Action
  ROI[ROI / Value Tracking] --> Monitor
